<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/18801AQTCDTTRMRJKMBPNNPMJSBLMGVQP> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "ABRA CADABRA";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$69.00 Per Person</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Attention all ABBA fans! Circle May 11, 2026 on your calendars because ABRA Cadabra – Celebrating the Music & Magic of ABBA, is making a spectacular return to Vernon after 2 years! Bring your mom and enjoy an unforgettable evening filled with iconic hits and cherished memories.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is an unmissable, family-friendly event suitable for all ages, featuring a dynamic live band, stunning vocals, captivating dancers, and authentic costumes. Prepare for an interactive stage extravaganza that will have you dancing, singing along, and reliving the magic of ABBA's greatest hits including Mamma Mia, Dancing Queen, Take A Chance, SOS, Waterloo, Fernando and many more!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>ABRA Cadabra has been wowing audiences worldwide for over 20 years, bringing the timeless music of ABBA to diverse audiences across continents. Their impressive résumé includes performances for the Malaysian Royal Family, iconic venues such as The Esplanade Theatre in Singapore, The Queen Elizabeth Theatre in Vancouver, Universal Studios in Florida and countless theatres and concert halls across North America and beyond.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Connect with ABRA Cadabra here:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Facebook: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ATributeToABBA\">www.facebook.com/ATributeToABBA</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Instagram: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ATributeToABBA\">www.instagram.com/ATributeToABBA</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Web-site: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.iloveabba.com\">www.iloveabba.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Best show we've ever seen!” – Gilberte Nowlan – Moncton, NB<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“OMG!!! What a spectacular show last night in Saint John!!! Thank you and come back soon… PLEASE!!!” - Judy McNab – Saint John, NB<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“Labels like \"tribute\" band don't cut it with these people. Powerful, tight bang-on lite-em-up delivery with a real joy in the performance! I would go see them again anywhere, anytime!” - Rob Randall – White Rock, BC<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>“I wanted to give a giant thank you, thank you, thank you for your show in Kelowna. We had so much fun and enjoyed it so much that I can't even put it into words. We were all grinning ear to ear! You sounded so great and were so on point. From the bottom of my heart, thank you for giving us all such a fun, special evening”. Dylan & Cavelle Wurfel – Kelowna, BC
""";
