<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/35001ANDBMVNTNMQTQBCTTLTMVTJHVKBV> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Magic Men Australia";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$121.00 Ultra Premium - (Row A)<span><br/></span>$109.75 Premium - Lower House (Rows B-F)<span><br/></span>$95.25 Deluxe - Lower House (Rows G-H)<span><br/></span>$64.50 Standard - (Rows N-P & AA-KK)</span><span><br/></span>Includes all fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">The #1 Ladies Night Out</span>, Breaking Records Worldwide <span class=\"BoldText\">Magic Men</span> Australia is taking over the world, breaking attendance records across Australia, New Zealand, Europe, U.S South America and Canada, including over 6,500 screaming ladies at a single Ladies Night.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is global entertainment at its peak.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our 2026 tour all new production \"Feel The Magic\" presents TikTok and world-famous Instagram superstar <span class=\"BoldText\">Will Parfitt</span>, with a combined following of over 20 million.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>He’s one of the most recognized male entertainers on social media… and he’s live on stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get ready for a night you’ll never forget.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Magic Men</span> delivers Australia’s most talented performers, high-energy choreography, jaw-dropping acrobatics, and cheeky crowd interaction, all packaged into a world-class touring production.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This isn’t just a show. It’s an experience. Expect:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li> - Record-breaking performances across the globe</li><li> - Featuring Will Parfitt (20M+ followers)</li><li> - World-class dance routines</li><li> - High-energy group numbers + unforgettable solos</li><li> - Charisma, comedy & crowd interaction</li><li> - A safe, inclusive, feel-good atmosphere</li><li> - VIP meet & greet + photo opportunities</li></ul><span><br/></span>Whether it’s a hen's night, birthday, girls’ night, or a chance to escape reality, Magic Men delivers a night that’s classy, powerful, and completely unforgettable.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Magic Men Australia</span>: Where entertainment meets energy and where records keep getting broken.
""";
