<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/5275ACTCRPTMBNPNRVPGKGGSCJJRDBDJG> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Merry Marching Band";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$16.00 All Seats</span><span><br/></span>Includes fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">They’re Back!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Straight from Underpantsburg, <span class=\"BoldText\">The Merry Marching Band</span> is a musical joyride like no other! What do you get when a pompous (and slightly clueless) bandleader leads a rowdy brass band on a whirlwind tour from Rio to the Red Planet? A high-energy explosion of music, mischief, and clowning that will have young audiences laughing, grooving, and drumming along.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Combining world music with theatrical clowning, vibrant brass instruments, and playful choreography, <span class=\"BoldText\">The Merry Marching Band</span> takes young audiences on a joyfully chaotic journey—from the rhythms of Brazil to the harmonies of Ukraine, and even the beats of outer space. Each stop bursts with rhythm, colour, and culture, brought to life by a cast of top-notch musicians and wacky surprises at every turn.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Part musical discovery, part comic adventure, this award-winning show sparks joy, wonder, and the uncontrollable impulse to turn your chair into a drum. Catch <span class=\"BoldText\">The Merry Marching Band</span> as they are on their way to the Vancouver International Children’s Festival!
""";
