<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/10401AVGBSHGLNCJKPBDLVSHHVCQHSBNR> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Michael Jackson HIStory Show";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$75.50 Adult <span><br/></span>$46.50 Child 13 & Under <span><br/></span>$70.50 Group 6+ Adult Ticket​</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Includes fees & charges</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss your chance to see Showtime’s The Michael Jackson HIStory Show - returning to Canada in 2026 to commemorate 30 years since Michael Jackson’s final, ground-breaking world tour: HISTORY.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This smash hit international tribute concert will be playing Vernon and District Performing Arts Centre, May 20th 2026.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get the full Michael Jackson concert experience with triple-threat performer Garth Field – electrifying in his role as Jackson – plus a live band, choreographed dancers, authentic costumes, state-of-the-art sound and theatrical lighting, vision and FX. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Hear Thriller, Billie Jean, Smooth Criminal, Bad, Beat It, ABC, Don’t Stop Til You Get Enough, Human Nature, PYT, They Don’t Really Care About Us and many more performed live on stage. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If you’ve been waiting for the concert event of the year… THIS IS IT! BOOK NOW! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*This is a tribute show and is not associated with the Estate of Michael Jackson.
""";
