<http://www.spektrix.com/ticketseller/event/31002AHNTDBKVDTQCLLKBQBVTKLSMMNRL> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Music of Hans Zimmer & Others";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">$99.75 - Rows A – C<span><br/></span>$89.75 - Rows D – J and AA to CC<span><br/></span>$79.75 - Rows K – P<span><br/></span></span><span class=\"BoldText\">$69.75 - Rows DD – KK</span><span><br/></span>Including fees & charges<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">The Music of Hans Zimmer & Others</span> - presented by a Pirates of the Caribbean star! Experience the unique and best film scores from Top Gun, James Bond, Pirates of the Caribbean, The Lion King, Gladiator, The Dark Knight, Inception, Interstellar and more, plus Dune and many other top productions ☠ — in a breathtaking concert featuring The Hollywood Film Orchestra & choir, star soloists and selected film clips!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Including the Oscar-winning, extraordinary soundscapes!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Enjoy the only film music concert series in the world with a presenter from the films, who will not only present the best music of Hans Zimmer, but also be available for a free picture with you if you buy your tickets today!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Immerse yourself in the musical universe of Hans Zimmer and secure your tickets now if still available!
""";
